@title Leadership Patterns Underpinning the Transformation Cycle
@sigils [🚴/旦 🌄/化]
@illustrates ["Different units (researchers, librarians, IT, governance, funders)" "have complementary strengths rather than identical roles."]
@illustrates ["IT’s constraints differ from REF’s; governance differs from researchers’."]
